@{
    ViewBag.Title = "FAQs";
}

<div class="container">
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <h4>We have the answers you seek, but can you handle the truth?</h4>

    <br />

    <div class="alert alert-warning alert-dismissible" role="alert">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span><span class="sr-only">Close</span></button>
        If you have any questions this is your first stop. If you cannot find an answer to your question make sure to contact us at support@chimaeraconspiracy.com.
    </div>

    <div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
        <div class="faqHeader">General</div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseOne">Do I need to register an account?</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseOne" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    No you do not, we understand what a pain it is to have to register a new account. You shouldn't need an account to keep track of your order,
                    all necessary details to access your order history and status will be made readily available to you in a secure anonymous fashion.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseEight">Can I recommend new products/designs?</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseEight" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    Absolutely! We're open to suggestions for what you'd like to see more of, whether it be a specific animal or theme for a new design 
                    or a new shirt color you'd like to see an existing design on. You can grab our ears via our Twitter handle or through our support
                    email, support@chimaeraconspiracy.com.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
        <div class="faqHeader">Shop</div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTwo">How does it all work?</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseTwo" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    Like most web stores you pick items and put them in a cart, then proceed through checkout. This process proceeds as follows:
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    <ol>
                        <li>We ask for your shipping address, this is used to calculate the cost of shipping as well as, of course, shipping the order to you.</li>
                        <li>Once a valid shipping address is entered we redirect you to Paypal to enter your payment details. We have no access to those details 
                            nor do we wish to, we let the pros at Paypal handle all that.</li>
                        <li>After entering your payment information you are redirected back to a confirmation page where you're able to see your order summary.
                            This is so you can confirm the details of your order and see the grand total before agreeing.</li>
                        <li>The order is then stored as "Pending" on our end until our tracker confirms the Paypal transaction is complete. A confirmation email
                            is sent to you.</li>
                        <li>When the Paypal transaction is complete we send the order request to our printers and update it as "Processing" on our end.</li>
                        <li>The order should be printed and shipped in roughly a week, once it ships you will receive a follow-up email containing tracking information.</li>
                        <li>Your order should arrive within 1-2 weeks, on average, from you placing the order.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseThree">How do I check my order status?</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseThree" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    After placing your order you should receive a confirmation email in the format of "chimaeraconspiracy.com/checkout/history/{Your unique and secret order identifier here}"
                    which will bring you a summary of your order and its progress through our system. This should contain details concerning the items ordered, shipping address,
                    totals calculated, current order status, and even tracking information if the order is shipped.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFour">What if I want to cancel?</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseFour" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    Once an order's status proceeds to "Processing", the request has been sent up to our printers. At this stage we're unable to cancel the order as the items have already
                    been paid for and are being created. You are however able to make a return by mailing it to us within 30 days of placing the order, just be sure to email us at
                    support@chimaeraconspiracy.com first so we can begin the return process proper.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseNine">What if my shirt doesn't come out right?</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseNine" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    If you're able to provide proof of the shirt's damage or misprint, either by picture or by mailing it in, we can offer a free replacement or simply reimburse you in full
                    for the order, buyer's choice. No hidden fees or shipping charges here!
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

