                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseSeven">When does my order ship?</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseSeven" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    Typically your order should ship roughly within a week of you placing the order but life can be unexpected and there may be delays. You can
                    always check the status of your order through the history link provided in your confirmation email but if it remains unshipped for longer
                    than a week feel free to reach out to us at support@chimaeraconspiracy.com and we'll be glad to let you know where our printer is at with
